dct_title_s: Hierosolymæ cvra neemiæ dvcis instavratæ descriptio
dct_alternative_sm: Hierosolymae cura neemiae ducis instauratae descriptio
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, vegetation, drainage, roads, places of historical interest; plan of Jerusalem.
